Name: My Landlord is a Futanari
About the game: Futa on Male Rent is due, and having recently been laid off, you seem to have found yourself in quite the pickle. Luckily your landlord is an older lady, who has taken a particular liking to you. Perhaps you can come to some kind of an arrangement? Read through some pretty raunchy(erotic) dialogue, accompanied by spicy nude depictions. Gameplay Kinetic Visual Novel H-Scenes ~5K words Immerse yourself in the story by typing in your own name, then proceeding to read through a raunchy story from the first-person perspective.
